[I sincerely hope that all the personnel carrying out the immunization
campaign, and any tourists to Ethiopia, get polio boosters before they go.
It is not generally appreciated that adults entering an outbreak area need
the extra protection of a booster, even if they were fully immunized as a
child. - Mod.JW]
